Mix @egg{1}, @ricotta{14%oz}, @nutmeg{1/4%tsp}, @lemon zest{1%lemon}, @Parmesan{1.5%oz}, and @flour{1%heaped Tbsp}.

Put 1 Tbsp @olive oil{1%Tbsp} into #frying pan{}. Scrape 8 dollops of mixture into pan and turn when golden.

Serve with favorite @marinara{}.
